s, forts, and plantation ruins from the 19th century.&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}\" id=\"mwKA\"><span about=\"#mwt12\">\n</span><div class=\"banner-image js-proportonal-resize notheme\" about=\"#mwt12\" id=\"mwKQ\" style=\"font-size: 108%;\">\n\t<p><span class=\"mw-default-size nolink interactiveIcon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><span><img resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:Interactive_icon.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Interactive_icon.svg/250px-Interactive_icon.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"133\" data-file-height=\"200\" data-file-type=\"drawing\" height=\"376\" width=\"250\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Interactive_icon.svg/500px-Interactive_icon.svg.png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span></p>\n\t<div class=\"mainpage-shadowbox notheme banner-box-2 banner-box-right\" style=\"width:45%\">\n        <div style=\"position:relative; float:left; margin:-4px;\">\n        <span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previous_Featured_travel_topics\" title=\"Previous Featured travel topics\"><img alt=\"FTT\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:Writing_Circle_white.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Writing_Circle_white.svg/40px-Writing_Circle_white.svg.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"20\" data-file-height=\"20\" data-file-type=\"drawing\" height=\"32\" width=\"32\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Writing_Circle_white.svg/120px-Writing_Circle_white.svg.png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></div>\n\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:1.25em;\" id=\"Featured_Travel_Topic\" class=\"mw-html-heading\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previous_Featured_travel_topics\" title=\"Previous Featured travel topics\">Featured Travel Topic</a></h2>\n        <h3 style=\"font-size:2em;\" id=\"Seminole_Wars\" class=\"mw-html-heading\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Seminole_Wars\" title=\"Seminole Wars\">Seminole Wars</a></h3>\n\t\t<div class=\"quote\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Seminole_Wars\" title=\"Seminole Wars\">A result of American settlement in the contested forests and prairies of colonial Florida, the devastating Seminole Wars fought between U.S. forces and Seminoles in Florida left behind wartime artifacts, forts, and plantation ruins from the 19th century.</a></div>\n\t</div>\n\t<p><span class=\"nolink\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Seminole Wars&quot;}\"><span title=\"Seminole Wars\"><img alt=\"Seminole Wars\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:SeminoleWarsBanner1.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/9/99/SeminoleWarsBanner1.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"1710\" data-file-height=\"570\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"567\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span>\n\t<span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Seminole Wars&quot;}\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Seminole_Wars\" title=\"Seminole Wars\"><img alt=\"Seminole Wars\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:SeminoleWarsBanner1.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/9/99/SeminoleWarsBanner1.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"1710\" data-file-height=\"570\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"567\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></p>\n</div>","link":"https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previous_Featured_travel_topics","retrieved":1761269123154}]}